126
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:26,000
We should remain hopeful.

127
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,040
Look.

128
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:30,200
Like the light above us here,

129
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:32,040
