214
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,160
They are from Siqi.

215
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,760
Hello, Siqi.

216
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:17,160
Xia Yuan.

217
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:20,480
